public class ThinkifyTaglist
extends java.util.ArrayList<ThinkifyTag>

ThinkifyTaglist extends from ArrayList, for holding onto a ordered collection of ThinkifyTag objects. Additional methods were added to this class for initializing the list based on a taglist string from a reader, and updating the list based on new tag data.

Author:
David Krull

Constructor Detail

ThinkifyTaglist

public ThinkifyTaglist()

ThinkifyTaglist

public ThinkifyTaglist(java.lang.String taglistString)
Initializes this ThinkifyTaglist, using the \r\n-separated string of taglist data received directly from the reader. Each line of taglistString is split off and parsed into a ThinkifyTag, which is then added to this ThinkifyTaglist.

Parameters:
taglistString - the raw taglist data from the reader
Method Detail

updateFromTagString

public void updateFromTagString(java.lang.String tagLine)
Parses a single "TAG=" line of tag data from the reader, creates a ThinkifyTag for that line, and adds/updates this ThinkifyTaglist with that new data.

Parameters:
tagLine - the single line of raw tag data from the reader

updateFromTaglistString

public void updateFromTaglistString(java.lang.String taglistString)
Parses an entire \r\n-separated string of taglist data received directly from the reader, creates ThinkifyTags for each line, and adds/updates this ThinkifyTaglist with the new data.

Parameters:
taglistString - the raw taglist data from the reader

addTag

public void addTag(ThinkifyTag newTag)
Adds the given newTag to this ThinkifyTaglist. This may produce duplicate entries in the ThinkifyTaglist with the same EPC. To merge new data into existing tag entries, use updateTag() instead.

Parameters:
newTag - the ThinkifyTag to add to this ThinkifyTaglist

updateTag

public void updateTag(ThinkifyTag newTag)
If the given newTag already exists in this ThinkifyTaglist, the new information is merged with the existing tag entry, using ThinkifyTag.update(). If the newTag doesn't already exist, it is added to this ThinkifyTaglist.

Parameters:
newTag - the ThinkifyTag data to add/merge
